Package: E3ExpressionShiny
Title: Shiny Explorer for E3 Expression Atlas Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Peter", "Thorpe", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "p.thorpe@dundee.ac.uk")
    )
Description: A modular Shiny application for querying and visualising
    Expression Atlas-derived expression and sample metadata tables generated
    by the E3 expression downloader pipeline. The application uses
    duckplyr/DuckDB-backed lazy queries and is intended to remain extensible
    for additional project data sources.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
